description: The Chrysalis is the undisputed pride of the Terran fleet - a magnificent vessel, with its unique mix of power, size and Terran-style grace. Even when designing a ship more akin to a moving city, the Terrans did not forget to give the vessel the visual polish it deserved. The Chrysalis served the Terran Colonial Union well when arriving through the Gateway; as the TCU’s colonization phase slowed, they began to appear in public and private auctions.
abilities: [{'ship_ability_id': 1, 'name': 'Integrated Hyperscan', 'description': 'Activating the Terran Integrated Hyperscan explores all hexes adjacent to the vehicle, and can be used once every five days.', 'type': 'active', 'value': 1, 'image_path': 'integrated-hyperscan.png', 'sound_path': 'Voidsweeper.m4a'}]
